strings: <voice_0x01001818><se_low>jungmi: So I decided to join Dragova's trial.
<voice_0x01001819><se_low>jungmi: I look forward to following you as a colleague.
<voice_0x0100181A><se_low>jungmi: Not a requirement. We've come a long way, I'm with you all the way!
<voice_0x0100181B><se_low>jungmi: So let's go. A celestial platform where the gods of Dragovia await!
<voice_0x0100181C><se_low>jungmi: I must secretly admit that in this temple there are the remains of Trianon and Zion.
<voice_0x0100181D><se_low>jungmi: It seems natural that we suffer and bury them together ...
<voice_0x0100181E><se_low>jungmi: He built an empty tomb in the labyrinth to hide the truth from his people.
